      <link>https://clarewest.github.io/blog/post/rstudio-global-2021-summarise/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Jan 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://clarewest.github.io/blog/post/rstudio-global-2021-summarise/</guid>
      <description>rstudio’s annual conference went online and global this year, which meant that I could attend for the first time. There were lots of interesting talks, and it was great to see familiar faces from GitHub/Twitter avatars come to life! This is a summary of the notes I took during the talks I attended, I will add links to the full talks on the rstudio website when they become available.</description>
